A joyful spring meadow at golden hour in Studio Ghibli style, featuring a family of wild rabbits nestled among vibrant wildflowers and decorated eggs hidden in tall grass. Cherry blossom petals drift through warm afternoon light, while butterflies dance above daffodils and tulips in full bloom. Soft watercolor textures, gentle rolling hills in the background with a single blooming tree silhouetted against a peachy-pink sky. The scene radiates warmth, renewal, and the gentle magic of seasonal celebration.
